  "strategy": [
    "Prioritize marker_seen: immediately switch to marker_track state to approach marker.",
    "If marker_lost during tracking, switch to scan_full to reacquire marker.",
    "On marker_close, always transition to goal_stop where only stop is allowed.",
    "After any obstacle encounter, pass through scan_full before resuming exploration.",
    "In obs_left, prefer rotate_commit_cw; in obs_right, prefer rotate_commit_ccw to avoid oscillations.",
    "In clear, allow both move_forward and full_rotate to alternate exploration and scanning.",
    "All action/commit states are one-shot: after action, return to decision/perception state.",
    "All uncontrollable events are total: every state has an outgoing transition for each uncontrollable.",
    "No infinite controllable loops; all helper/action states return to a main state after action.",
    "No move_forward from obs_front; always require recovery via scan_full after obstacle."
  ]
